assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Lihit Lab.,Inc. manufactures and sells office supplies in Japan and internationally. It offers punch and staple files; Z-type, slide bar and bookbinding, clear holder, pocket holder, and other files; clear books; binders; card, postcard, photo album, and bankbook holders; clip type files; clear, file, and document cases; P.P. and sewing bags; bag-in-bag products, bag hangers, shoulder belts, and accessory pouches; pencil cases; and notebooks, notebook accessories, and twist ring binding tools. The company also provides desk and bookend stands, partition boards, magnetic pocket racks, box files, organizing supplies, office supplies, slide cutters, and steel equipment, as wells as optional parts for electric drills and punches; medical supplies comprising mask cases, hospital pouches, medicine cases, nursing care record files, medical record folder racks, card indexes, medical record books, laminate films, face shields, medicine labels, bed plates, meal tags, bed plate name cards, and ointment case labels. In addition, it is involved in the real estate rental business. Lihit Lab.,Inc. was founded in 1938 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan.
